               <p>JOSEPH LLOYD. I live in <placeName id="t18340904-170-crimeloc953">Bartlett's-buildings, Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18340904-170-crimeloc953" type="placeName" value="Bartlett's-buildings, Holborn"></interp>
